                    <li class="mb-3 text-dark text-justify" style="font-size: 11pt">process your request,</li>
                    <li class="mb-3 text-dark text-justify" style="font-size: 11pt">perform analytics, debug and conduct research,</li>
                    <li class="mb-3 text-dark text-justify" style="font-size: 11pt">provide customer service, training,</li>
                    <li class="mb-3 text-dark text-justify" style="font-size: 11pt">send you messages, updates, security alerts, and account notifications,</li>
                    <li class="mb-3 text-dark text-justify" style="font-size: 11pt">if you provide us with your contacts’ information, such as your friends or co-travelers, we may process this information: (i) to facilitate your referral invitations, (ii) to share your trip details and facilitate trip planning, (iii) for fraud detection and prevention, and (iv) to facilitate your requests or for any other purpose you authorize,</li>
                    <li class="mb-3 text-dark text-justify" style="font-size: 11pt">personalize and customize your experience based on your interactions with the EZV2Villa Platform, your search and booking history, your profile information and preferences, and other content you submit, and</li>
                    <li class="mb-3 text-dark text-justify" style="font-size: 11pt">enable your use of our enterprise products.</li>
